#summary PLACEHOLDER Developer's Guide: TBSModel.java

= Introduction =
[TBSModel.java] is the superclass for the two Model objects representing the data under inspection. The two Models - [StudentModel] and [AdminModel] - have somewhat different ways of handling data due to the differing needs of the two classes of users.
